1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
Three days ago, one bite would've shattered her.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:06,000
So you finally couldn't hold back?

3
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:14,000
You're not spirit energy... you're a demon! How are you THIS strong?!

4
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:21,000
So fast... I underestimated this she-demon.

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:26,000
Toxin detected. Demon blood auto-neutralizing.

6
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:29,000
Impossible! My venom drops even Golden Core cultivators!

7
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:34,000
That's the one spot on its body with no scales.

8
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:40,000
You wanted to eat me, didn't you? Go on. Eat.

9
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:43,000
Mercy! I'll submit — I can help you take down the Empress!

10
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:46,000
When you ate them, did you ever show mercy?

11
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:53,000
Great demon slain. Bloodline now LV2 — Silver Rank! Skill unlocked: Frost Control.

12
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:56,000
Mercy, my lady! I only steal scraps — I've never eaten anyone!

13
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:59,000
From today, you work for me.

14
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:04,000
From this day on, the cold palace has one master.

15
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:09,000
My lady... did you become a goddess?

16
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:13,000
Not a goddess. Something far more terrifying.
